{"tid":1818132,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"［你唔係唔寫呀］幫還押手足打氣 一齊寫新年卡！","createTime":"2020-01-09T15:48:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-09T23:46:37.000Z","uid":611,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"be1762977b8302a2fd295f9990b5002727b2f207","tid":1818132,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:48:55.000Z","msg":"上個Post見到有啲巴絲都想寫信幫手足打氣<br />\n<br />\n幫幫手,請還押手足過年食好啲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1814332\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1814332</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n開返個新Post希望可以收集到巴絲嘅一啲打氣信或者打氣句子又或者係畫都可以 <br />\n<br />\n我會集合埋下星期一寄出 <br />\n有心想寫嘅巴絲 可以寫完之後TG畀我 <br />\n我會印出黎寄畀手足 <br />\n<br />\n下面有手足女朋友上個月寄畀佢封信嘅一部分<br />\n大家唔好介意佢寫殘體 佢讀書果陣成日寫字慣咗手勢 我會屌屌佢架啦 ！佢呢家已經受咗教訓架啦！<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FpqOkio.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFpqOkio.jpg&h=7c622ec6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寫完可以TG畀我 <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/writeletteraddoil\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fwriteletteraddoil&d=eKFc4b3FQa1ReKUUeYtKdBphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=52b2a55c\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/writeletteraddoil</a><br />\n<br />\n代手足多謝咁多位巴絲先！"},{"pid":"00f864e3cf2c97f38550740e3cb0acd97bdcceec","tid":1818132,"uid":163704,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:49:14.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n[全港最大的Fact Check平台-非食店篇]集合超過400間各地區各行業的良心店<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1817378\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1817378</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6519cb3f3dc78c0053830d002f05916d25163afe","tid":1818132,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:49:28.000Z","msg":"岩岩開咗係創意台 一個人都無 試吓開多次 再無人就算啦"},{"pid":"ca0ea947bb36bbb4783e5accf2ff0efd2ce80cbe","tid":1818132,"uid":611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T15:50:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ca373e59084f00e802272cb208acfdb1f41d5826","tid":1818132,"uid":188685,"like